------------------------------------------------------------------------------
ORIGINAL WORK
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
The Sentinel runtime (SentinelCore, SentinelSkin), the sensors, the Council,
the Deck/Bridge, the safety substrate, and the supporting services are original
work authored for this project.

------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INDICATORS IMPLEMENTING PUBLIC METHODS (original code)
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
These implement publicly-published trading methods/formulas (methods and formulas
are not copyrightable); the *code* is original to this project:
  - Average Directional Index (ADX/DMI, Wilder)   -> Sentinel ADXPro
  - Woodies CCI (Ken Wood's method)               -> Sentinel WoodiesCCIPro
  - TrendMagic-style ATR/CCI trailing line        -> Sentinel Trend
  - Candle-grammar reversal method                -> Sentinel God Reversal
  - Buy/sell volume pressure                      -> Sentinel BSVPMountain
  - Ground-up volatility envelope                 -> Sentinel VolEnvelope
  - Waddah Attar Explosion method (public)        -> Sentinel WAE (v2, clean-room)
  - SuperTrend / VIDYA (Chande) / Parabolic SAR (Wilder) / ADXVMA / regime &
    structure statistics / Leledc exhaustion / harmonic Fib ratios -> the extra
    Sentinel sensors (clean-room from public formulae; any installed reference
    indicator was surveyed for concept only, no code copied)
  - Public moving-average & filter formulae (SMA/EMA/WMA/VWMA/DEMA/TEMA/HMA and the
    zero-lag family; Ehlers Super Smoother/Gaussian/Butterworth) -> Sentinel Smoothers

