------------------------------------------------------------------------------
PROVENANCE NOTES
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
  - Sentinel WAE was formerly a port of unlicensed NT-community / TradingView code
    (LazyBear -> shayankm -> donto -> karmic913). That version (SentinelWAE_v1_0_0)
    was RETIRED and replaced (2026-07-11) with a CLEAN-ROOM implementation
    (SentinelWAE_v2_0_0) written from the public Waddah Attar formula using
    NinjaTrader's own EMA/StdDev/ATR (listed under "public methods" above). No
    third-party code remains in the shipped WAE.
  - Provenance was audited per sensor on 2026-07-11 (headers read + sources checked);
    every shipped sensor is either original work, an original implementation of a
    public method, or an MPL-2.0 component with attribution.

